{"tid":2253642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"滙豐杜嘉祺：冀在內地拓展業務　探索新投資機會","createTime":"2020-10-22T09:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T09:51:29.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b464ed9cda6b8c38471a9c8ebfa1d40c4100960e","tid":2253642,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:49:28.000Z","msg":"滙豐杜嘉祺：冀在內地拓展業務 探索新投資機會<br />\n<br />\n滙豐控股(00005)主席杜嘉祺(Mark Tucker)近日參與上海市市長國際企業家諮詢視頻會議時稱，期待在中國市場探索新的投資機會。滙豐將繼續積極參與上海深化「五個中心」建設，並為中國金融市場的進一步開放和發展貢獻一份力量。<br />\n杜嘉祺表示，在增強城市發展韌性、適應新形勢變化方面，上海既有發展的先機，又有成功的優勢，包括其不斷加強的區域合作和完善的科技和基建投資體系。同時，在城市建設方面，上海也正在向創新、創業、數字技術和可持續方向穩步推進。<br />\n他續稱，滙豐十分期待在上海以及更廣泛的中國市場進一步拓展業務，並探索新的投資機會。伴隨着中國金融市場的持續開放和發展，滙豐許多客戶的相關業務取得了較大增長。又認為，中國金融科技和創新日新月異，均為國際金融機構在中國的發展提供了寶貴的機遇。"},{"pid":"889f04acb7911700bd4fad7a9559535374c27eee","tid":2253642,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"繼續跪，繼續瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20cd8a83f826be26c4bd0e76ce7c259bf3318cf","tid":2253642,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:50:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201020/mobile/bkn-20201020141533755-1020_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201020%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201020141533755-1020_00842_001.html&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPdOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=370e7f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201020/mobile/bkn-20201020141533755-1020_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"24511913b70efbafeaded498bf79a790c0a27c90","tid":2253642,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"老貓：drop to zero<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c804ccbb412bb769cebd83f0834ae83a3284beb3","tid":2253642,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"股價探索新低位機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}